<h3 id="topic_head">Academic Honesty</h3>
<div>
<div class="honor_topic_content first">
<h3>WHAT</h3>
<p>We agree to be completely honest in all our dealings, including class assignments and tests. This means we don't plagiarize material, fabricate or falsify information, or cheat.</p>
</div>
<div class="honor_topic_content last">
<h3>WHY</h3>
<p>Being truthful with ourselves and others is a principle of the gospel of Jesus Christ and a central feature of the CES Honor Code. When we are honest in all things, we promise to obey all of these principles fully without compromises. Besides being dishonest, cheating on your schoolwork hurts others, reduces the confidence in receiving a fair eduction and greatly reduces personal growth and abilities.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
